"explanation": "Definitions:\n• Sound — a form of energy which causes sensation of hearing in our ears\n• Frequency — usually represented by symbol v (Greek letter nu)\n\nAlso know:\n• Materials Required is defined as A steel bucket (or an earthen pitcher) and arrangement of water flowing from a water tap.\n• Procedure: Take an empty steel bucket or an earthen pitcher and place it below a water tap.\n• Observation: You will observe that as the water level in the bucket.\n• Observation is defined as You will observe that as the water level in the bucket.",
