"explanation": "Also know:\n• Again, rub the glass rod with silk cloth and then bring the silk cloth near the bits of.\n• Rubbing the glass rod with silk cloth.\n• Glass rod and silk cloth attract pieces of paper.\n• Observation and conclusion: It means that charges are produced on both glass rod as well as silk cloth when these are rubbed together.",
