"content": "Aim: To show that like charges repel each other\n\n• A charged body can attract small bits of paper, straw and dry leaves.\n• Materials Required: A glass rod, a silk cloth, small bits of paper, a silk thread and another glass rod.\n• Materials Required is defined as A glass rod, a silk cloth, small bits of paper, a silk thread and another glass rod.\n• Suspend this charged glass rod from a rigid support using a silk thread.\n• Bring another glass rod, after rubbing it with silk, near the suspended glass rod.",
